cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks related to video processing, such as artistic style transfer, enhancement, colorization, image-to-image translation, and intrinsic image decomposition. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes an end-to-end approach based on deep recurrent networks, which involves training a model to minimize losses and balance temporal stability and perceptual similarity. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.MM), learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and graphics (cs.GR).
